## Scope

The MIT license above covers:

- Source code in this repository (the React + Vite app under `app/`,
  the scraper, parser, concept-extraction pipeline, and match-scoring
  pipeline scripts under `app/scripts/`).
- Build-time documentation (`README.md`, `app/README.md`,
  `docs/superpowers/specs/`, `docs/superpowers/plans/`,
  `docs/assessments/`).
- Curated derivative artifacts produced by the offline pipelines
  (`app/data-source/concepts.json`, `app/data-source/profile-concepts.json`,
  `app/data-source/profile-field-concepts.json`,
  `app/data-source/matches.json`) — these are derivative works of the
  third-party content described below, generated by BioKEA's curation
  and LLM passes.

The license above does **not** cover:

- Raw scraped HTML in `detail-pages/`, `list-pages/`, and `manifest.json`.
  These pages were retrieved from the DOE Genesis Mission Partnership
  Exchange (https://partnerships.genesismissionconsortium.org/) and remain
  the property of the original profile authors and the program operators.
  They are included in this repository only to make the build pipeline
  reproducible. If you intend to use these pages or any individual partner
  profile beyond running this build, you should consult the original source
  and the relevant profile owners.
- The BioKEA logo and brand assets in `app/public/brand/`. These are owned
  by BioKEA and are included for the navigator's branding only; they are
  not licensed for use in derivative works without permission.
